TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));


Use \(C\) to denote \(\cos x\), and express 
$BR
 \(\cos(x+20,000\pi) = \) \{ ans_rule(12) \}
 in terms of \(C\). 
EOT

ANS(fun_cmp("C", vars=>["C"]));

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
$BR
Similarly, express
$BR
 \(\cos(x+20,001\pi) = \) \{ ans_rule(12) \}
 in terms of \(C\). 
EOT

ANS(fun_cmp("-C", vars=>["C"]));


